---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="订阅 - 一心" description="订阅本站更新">
  <div class="subscribe">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>订阅</h1>
    </div>

    <p>感谢你的关注！你可以通过以下方式订阅本站更新：</p>

    <section>
      <h2>RSS/Atom Feed</h2>
      <p>使用任何 RSS 阅读器订阅：</p>
      <div class="feed-url">
        <code>https://example.com/atom.xml</code>
        <button class="copy-btn" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('https://example.com/atom.xml'); alert('已复制!')">复制</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>订阅说明</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>本站文章更新频率不定，通常每周 1-2 篇。</li>
        <li>Feed 包含文章标题、摘要和链接。</li>
        <li>推荐使用 <a href="https://feedly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Feedly</a>、<a href="https://inoreader.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Inoreader</a> 等阅读器。</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .page-header {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.8em;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2D2D2D;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .feed-url {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: #F5F5F5;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .feed-url code {
      background-color: transparent;
      font-size: 0.85em;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .copy-btn {
      padding: 0.4em 0.8em;
      background-color: #005BBB;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.85em;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .copy-btn:hover {
      background-color: #1A5FB4;
    }

    li {
      color: #444444;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
